author: GameSpot
description:
We were that close to rage quitting...

After his humiliation at the hands' of his colleague Lucy, Kurt faces the challenge of using nothing but parries to beat four warriors, each with increasing difficulty, at the Hidden Gestral Arena. But here's the kicker: he's a complete beginner whose parry skills are either naturally fantastic or alarmingly flawed. To his rescue is his coach, who aims to provide him with the best advice during the harrowing trials. Will Kurt be able to pass all four challenges?
